{"tid":1250644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃之鋒—《我不是細路》","createTime":"2019-06-22T07:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T07:09:49.000Z","uid":220074,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6be45131583319e68f00f77be32a7f9f46b5819f","tid":1250644,"uid":220074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T07:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaD7p3J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaD7p3J.png&h=d4e386a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L0jFK3K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0jFK3K.png&h=bd9fbe0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tk2zPvq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTk2zPvq.png&h=41769248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n借朋友本書睇完，<br />\n希望可以分享俾你哋。<br />\n<br />\n希望香港人要繼續加油，<br />\n即使疲倦 都要努力爭取。<br />\n<br />\n感激你哋對香港嘅愛，<br />\n願意奮不顧身守護香港。<br />\n<br />\n無論你幾灰心幾絕望都唔好氣餒，加油"},{"pid":"d8d3e285173207f1d6dd4872b58bc9548e348ec9","tid":1250644,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T07:06:38.000Z","msg":"長期 = 聚散<br />\n不求一仗功成，但求齊上齊落"},{"pid":"367984d58fc0e0f4b410f86613e5432a2da9f374","tid":1250644,"uid":220074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T07:06:47.000Z","msg":"小時候，我會跟父母說：「呢度好多警察，我好安全！」<br />\n<br />\n長大後，我會跟父母說：「呢度好多警察，我好危險！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7506b3e7f52630839dc992a186913bc06f6bfd","tid":1250644,"uid":220074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T07:08:48.000Z","msg":"無爭取過嘅嘢永遠都唔會得到，<br />\n<br />\n但係只要你有嘗試過 至少有機會。"},{"pid":"90de60bc47f059b8150a9933c29c0208e71b78a4","tid":1250644,"uid":220074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T07:09:49.000Z","msg":"只希望可以打動更多人企出嚟 唔好啞忍俾政府踩住上"}]}